367→    <h1>Your personal agent activity&nbsp;feed</h1>
368→    <p class="subtitle">
369→      Not another orchestrator. A&nbsp;dashboard that makes sense of every session your AI agents have run — across repos, your home directory, notes, configs, everywhere.
370→    </p>
