390→          <span>Every session scoped to a single git repository</span>
391→        </div>
392→        <div class="problem-item them">
393→          <span class="icon">C</span>
394→          <span>Agents run in containers or worktrees — isolated from your machine context</span>
395→        </div>
396→        <div class="problem-item them">
397→          <span class="icon">C</span>
398→          <span>Must launch agents through their UI to get any visibility</span>
399→        </div>
400→        <div class="problem-item them">
401→          <span class="icon">C</span>
402→          <span>No view of non-repo work: dotfiles, notes, home&nbsp;directory&nbsp;tasks</span>
403→        </div>
404→      </div>
405→      <div class="problem-col">
406→        <h3>Agent Kitchen</h3>
407→        <div class="problem-item us">
408→          <span class="icon">AK</span>
409→          <span>Sessions grouped by repo <em>and</em> non-repo locations like ~/dotfiles, ~/notes</span>
410→        </div>
411→        <div class="problem-item us">
